            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken is cooked, add the <strong>chopped coriander stalks</strong> to the pan</p><p>Add your <strong>cultured coconut</strong> and the juice of <strong>half</strong> the<strong> lime[s]</strong> to the pan — this is your <strong>Thai-style free range chicken & coconut curry</strong></p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining lime</strong> into 1 wedge per person</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
