            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-copy-1703174667720-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Thai-style free range chicken & coconut curry</strong> with the<strong> basmati rice</strong> to the side</p><p>Garnish with the<strong> chopped peanuts</strong>, <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>coriander leaves</strong>, <strong>remaining chopped chilli </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!) and a <strong>lime wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
